# 副簽  
(pos:名詞)  
<explanation>  
yue: 唔係主簽名嘅人，而係第二個簽名嘅人，通常用嚟確認、輔助或見證主簽名者嘅決定（量詞：個）  
eng: co-signer; second signatory  

<eg>  
yue: 呢份合約要兩個老闆副簽人才算數。 (ni1 faan6 hap6 jek6 jiu3 loeng5 lou5 baai2 sin3 jan4 coi3 syun3.)  
eng: This contract needs two bosses to co-sign before it’s valid.  

yue: 呢張支票要你同財務副簽人才可以兌現。 (ni1 zang1 zi1 piu3 jiu3 nei5 tung4 coi4 syu6 faat3 jin4 coi3 sin3 jin4 coi3 sin3 jin4.)  
eng: This cheque needs you and the finance officer to co-sign before it can be cashed. [end of text]


